\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s22 \cs28\f3\cf6 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}on all Saturdays 
\par }\pard \s22\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs28\i\fs24\cf6\insrsid6574074 at Compline the Kontakion of the Resurrection is not read, but rather the one from the Triodion (except the fifth week of Lent).
